### 2-3. Call 도메인 (`catalog: maum`)

```kotlin
// domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/entity/call/CallRoomEntity.kt
@Entity
@Table(catalog = "maum", name = "call_room")
class CallRoomEntity(
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
    val id: String = "",

    @Column(nullable = false)
